      "date": "2019-08-09 03:52:27.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> Its in LU-11626 the details of a reproducer.\n > We could always have a follow on patch.\n\nThis patch doesn't fix LU-11626 (holding changelog device open during unmount), it only fixes the race from LU-12566 where the unmount code is traversing the changelog linked list while the mounting client is changing it.",
